data.description: *Seller to credit buyer $14,000 towards closing cost on the condition that buyer submits a full price offer* Live, Work and  Play in Kapolei! Your dream home which consists of a 3 Story, 4 Bedroom 3 bath flex home is located in the Mehana Nanala Community. This home has a 1 car garage with 2 additional parking spaces, stainless steel appliances, 2 lanais, and beautiful mountain views. The flex space on the 1st floor with a bathroom provides the flexibility of a commercial space  to run your home-based business or can be used as a recreational room or a 4th bedroom. The main floor has an  additional 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms with a balcony off the primary bedroom and the kitchen. Easy access to H-1  freeway, close to Kamakana Alii Mall and Kapolei Commons for your shopping, dining, and entertainment needs. Don’t miss  this opportunity to make this gem yours today!
